About Event

​Before we ring in the new year, we’re tearing things down — and building them back better.

​Join us at Frontier Makerspace for a full-day Space Hack Day focused on reorganizing, upgrading, and expanding the capabilities of the space. This is a hands-on, community-powered buildout where we optimize layouts, improve workflows, and prep the lab for everything coming in the new year.
